    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="poem" met= "-+|-+|-+|-+|" rhyme="ababccddeefghgaaiiifjfj">          
                <head type="title"><handShift new="#HANDJR1826-27" script="print" medium="ink"/>Not such the night</head>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Not such the night whose stormy might, <add rend= "linenumber-right">1160</add></l>
                    <l>Heroic <persName corresp="#BALMA">Balma</persName> braved,</l>
                    <l>When darken<del change= "character">ed</del> ning on the <geogName corresp="#GOUTES">Goutes</geogName> height,</l>
                    <l>The tempest howled and raved.</l>
                    <l>Upon the mighty hill forlorn</l>
                    <l>He stood alone amid the storm, <add rend= "linenumber-right">1165</add></l> 
                    <l>Watching the last day gleams decay</l>
                    <l>Supposing its returning ray,</l>
                    <l>Should see him lying there asleep</l>
                    <l>With <geogName corresp="#ALPINE">Alpine</geogName> snow for winding sheet.</l>
                    <l>Methinks I see him, as he stood, <add rend= "linenumber-right">1170</add></l> 
                    <l>Upon the ridge of snow,</l>
                    <l>The battering burst of winds above</l>
                    <l>The cloudy precipice below</l>
                    <l>Watching the dawn.  With proud delight</l>
                    <l>He saw that long <del rend="strikethrough">and</del> tempest<add type= "overwriting" place= "above"><space quantity="25" unit="chars"/>uous</add> night, <add rend= "linenumber-right">1175</add></l> 
                    <l>Drive to the westward, and unfold,</l>
                    <l>The ocean snowfields upwards rolled,</l>
                    <l>Bright with the mornings glance of gold,</l>
                    <l>It past away, the <del rend="strikethrough">headlong</del> tossing flood</l>
                    <l>Of changing vapour headlong riding <add rend= "linenumber-right">1180</add></l> 
                    <l>And lo, the untrodden summit stood,</l>
                    <l>Accessibly beside him,</l>
                </lg>
            </div>
